      "description": "Create a 3-foot planar blade in an unoccupied visible space within 60 feet for up to 1 minute with concentration. The caster makes up to two melee spell attacks with the blade when it appears and after each bonus-action movement, scores critical hits on 18 or higher, and the blade passes harmlessly through barriers.",
